Interface IPSCatalogSummary

All Known Implementing Classes:
PSAction, PSAgingTransition, PSAssemblyTemplateWs, PSAutoTranslation, PSCommunity, PSDisplayFormat, PSItemDefinition, PSItemDefSummary, PSKeyword, PSLocale, PSRelationshipConfig, PSRole, PSSearch, PSState, PSTransition, PSTransitionBase, PSWorkflow
public interface IPSCatalogSummary
extends IPSCatalogIdentifier

Provides a subset of information about a catalog object. This represents an object but is not an object itself. Objects implement IPSCatalogItem.
